   Croatian Chamber Commerce, Zagreb},
Abstract = {Objectives of this work are to research, present and propose model of
   informational aspects of all trends of operational research included in
   the criminal intelligence analysis. Research is done as part of
   operational research modelling used for intelligent and classical
   software solutions proposed and used in the development of the
   Intelligent information system for the Croatian Anti Money Laundering
   Department and for the Croatian Criminal police. The study analyses
   objectives with methods of operational research, artificial intelligence
   and other methods. Conclusion is that software solutions must obey
   trends of operational research modelling in informational aspects of the
   criminal intelligence analysis involved. Important is to use the
   appropriate software tools in dealing with the criminal incident, or the
