Year = {2018},
Volume = {86},
Pages = {598-602},
Month = {SEP},
Abstract = {With the rapid development of information technology, especially network
   technology, people's ability to collect, store and transmit data are
   increasing. The data have exploded in an explosive manner. In sharp
   contrast, the ability to make valuable data for decision making is very
   poor. In this paper, data mining is the most basic problem. In order to
   overcome the shortcomings of the traditional clustering algorithm for
   k-means clustering, it is difficult to determine the initial clustering
   center and the k-means algorithm is improved. When determining the
   initial K-, the convergence factor is improved and the global optimum is
   achieved, so as to realize the determination of clustering center. By
   using improved k-means algorithm to approximate the criminal data, the
   validity of this method is verified. (C) 2018 Elsevier B.V. All rights
   reserved.},
